    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Gamasiphis angaridis sp. n. Female. 1. Lateral (antiaxial) view of chelicera; 2. Epistome: A – B variations of shape; 3. Hypostome; 4. Corniculi; 5. Dorsal idiosoma; 6. Ventral idiosoma; 7. Spermatheca." ;
